<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>ParkerPixiePaws • Cozy Amigurumi, Handmade with Heart</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Cozy amigurumi from ParkerPixiePaws — soft, squishy, and stitched with love. Commission a custom friend or browse Handmade Highlights & Pixie Projects. Item of the Month is pumpkin pals for $15." />

  <!-- Fav / Share -->
  <link rel="icon" href="/CapyGoldIcon.png" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="ParkerPixiePaws — Cozy Amigurumi" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Soft, squishy friends — stitched with love. Commission customs or grab the Item of the Month for $15." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://parkerpixie.netlify.app/amigurumi/" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://parkerpixie.netlify.app/img/parkerpixiepawprofile.png" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />

  <style>
    :root{
      --bg: #faf7fb;
      --panel: #ffffff;
      --ink: #3a3042;
      --subtle: #6e6274;
      --brand: #7c6ac8;
      --brand-2: #e9d8fd;
      --accent: #e7b3c2;
      --glow: 0 10px 24px rgba(60, 40, 120, .12);
      --radius: 18px;
      --radius-lg: 26px;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html,body{height:100%}
    body{ 
      margin:0; 
      color:var(--ink); 
      font: 16px/1.55 system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji"; 
      letter-spacing:.2px;
      background: url('/img/pawback.png') no-repeat center center fixed;
      background-size: cover;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px){
      body {
        background: url('/img/pawbackmobile.png') no-repeat center center fixed;
        background-size: cover;
      }
    }
    img{max-width:100%; display:block}
    a{color:var(--brand); text-decoration:none}
    a:hover{text-decoration:underline}

    .wrap{max-width:1100px; margin:auto; padding:22px}

    header{ position:relative; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow:hidden; box-shadow: var(--glow); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }
    .hero{display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr; gap:20px; align-items:center; padding:32px 28px}
    @media (max-width: 880px){ .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr; padding:24px} }

    .hero-copy h1{margin:0 0 8px; font-size: clamp(28px, 3.6vw, 44px); letter-spacing:.3px}
    .hero-copy p{margin:0 0 16px; color:var(--subtle)}
    .badges{display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin:10px 0 18px}
    .badge{background:var(--panel); border:1px solid #eee; padding:6px 10px; border-radius:999px; font-size:12px; color:var(--subtle)}
    .cta-row{display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap}
    .btn{display:inline-block; padding:12px 16px; border-radius:12px; font-weight:600; border:1px solid transparent; box-shadow: var(--glow)}
    .btn.primary{background: var(--brand); color:#fff}
    .btn.primary:hover{filter:brightness(1.05)}
    .btn.ghost{background:#fff; border-color:#eee; color:var(--ink)}

    .hero-art{position:relative}
    .cloud{ position:absolute; inset:auto auto 10% -10%; width:120%; height:70%; z-index:0; background: radial-gradient(300px 140px at 20% 30%, rgba(124,106,200,.22), transparent 60%), radial-gradient(360px 160px at 80% 60%, rgba(231,179,194,.20), transparent 60%); filter: blur(24px); }
    .hero-img{position:relative; z-index:1; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: var(--glow); border: 6px solid #fff}

    section{margin:28px 0}
    .card{background:var(--panel); border:1px solid #eee; border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--glow)}
    .section-head{display:flex; align-items:baseline; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; margin:0 0 14px}
    .section-head h2{margin:0; font-size: clamp(20px, 2.6vw, 28px)}
    .section-head p{margin:4px 0 0; color:var(--subtle)}

    .iotm{display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap:22px; padding:22px}
    @media (max-width: 820px){ .iotm{grid-template-columns:1fr} }
    .price{font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 28px); font-weight:800; color:var(--brand)}
    .chips{display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap}
    .chip{padding:6px 10px; border-radius:999px; background:var(--brand-2); color:#4b3f7f; font-size:12px}
    .iotm .btn{margin-top:10px}

    .grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr); gap:14px}
    .g-item{grid-column: span 4; border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid #eee; background:#fff; box-shadow: var(--glow)}
    .g-item img{aspect-ratio:1/1; object-fit:cover}
    .g-item .cap{padding:10px; font-size:14px; color:var(--subtle)}
    @media (max-width: 900px){ .g-item{grid-column: span 6} }
    @media (max-width: 560px){ .g-item{grid-column: span 12} }

    .steps{display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap:14px; padding:24px}
    @media (max-width: 800px){ .steps{grid-template-columns:1fr} }
    .step{padding:16px; border:1px solid #eee; border-radius:16px; background:#fff}
    .k{display:inline-grid; place-items:center; width:34px; height:34px; border-radius:10px; background:var(--brand-2); color:#4b3f7f; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px}

    details{border:1px solid #eee; border-radius:12px; padding:12px 14px; background:#fff}
    details + details{margin-top:10px}
    summary{cursor:pointer; font-weight:600}
    summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}

    footer{margin:26px 0 40px; color:var(--subtle); text-align:center}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <header class="card">
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <h1>ParkerPixiePaws — Cozy Amigurumi</h1>
          <p>Soft, squishy friends stitched with intention. I make capybaras, chickens, puffins, pelicans, and custom creatures that feel like a hug.</p>
          <div class="badges">
            <span class="badge">Handmade in Madison, WI</span>
            <span class="badge">Crafted and perfected with YOU in mind</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-row">
            <a class="btn primary" href="#commission">Commission an Amigurumi</a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="#gallery">Browse Amigurumi</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-art">
          <div class="cloud" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <img class="hero-img" src="/img/ParkerPixiePawProfile.png" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='/img/hero.jpg';" alt="ParkerPixiePaws profile collage of cozy amigurumi."/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section id="iotm" class="card">
      <div class="iotm">
        <div>
          <div class="section-head">
            <h2>✨ Item of the Month</h2>
          </div>
          <p>This month: <strong>Pocket Pumpkins</strong> — plump, palm-sized cuties perfect for fall trays, teacher gifts, or anxiety squishes. Just pick your favorite color!</p>
          <div class="chips">
            <span class="chip">Made to order</span>
            <span class="chip">Ships in 3–5 days</span>
            <span class="chip">Approx. 3.5&quot; wide</span>
          </div>
          <p class="price">$15 • Shipping available at shipping costs</p>
          <a class="btn primary" href="https://forms.gle/YOUR_COMMISSION_FORM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Order a Pumpkin</a>
          <p style="margin-top:8px; color:var(--subtle); font-size:14px">Limited batch. When sold out, the button will be disabled.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/img/pumpkin.jpg" alt="Hand holding a crocheted pumpkin in front of a pile of amigurumi pumpkins." />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="gallery" aria-labelledby="gal-h">
      <div class="section-head"><h2 id="gal-h">✨ Handmade Highlights & Pixie Projects</h2><p>Textures, colors, and cozy vibes.</p></div>
      <div class="grid">
        <figure class="g-item"><img src="/img/bejeweled.png" alt="Amigurumi peacock with jeweled tail."><figcaption class="cap">Bejeweled the Peacock</figcaption></figure>
        <figure class="g-item"><img src="/img/bonnie.jpg" alt="Amigurumi chicken in cream and gold."><figcaption class="cap">Bonnie the Chicken</figcaption></figure>
        <figure class="g-item"><img src="/img/gilligan.jpg" alt="Amigurumi character Gilligan."><figcaption class="cap">Gilligan</figcaption></figure>
        <figure class="g-item"><img src="/img/ginny.jpg" alt="Amigurumi character Ginny."><figcaption class="cap">Ginny</figcaption></figure>
        <figure class="g-item"><img src="/img/grogu.jpg" alt="Amigurumi Grogu with big ears."><figcaption class="cap">Grogu</figcaption></figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="commission" class="card" aria-labelledby="how-h">
      <div class="section-head"><h2 id="how-h">How Commissions Work</h2><p>Simple, cozy steps.</p></div>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step"><div class="k">1</div><strong>Tell me your idea.</strong><br/>Animal, vibe, size, colors — or show a reference pic.</div>
        <div class="step"><div class="k">2</div><strong>I confirm details + price.</strong><br/>Most are complete within 2 to 3 weeks!</div>
        <div class="step"><div class="k">3</div><strong>I Stitch, I deliver.</strong><br/>You can pick it up, arrange to meet, or I can ship it to you if you agree to pay the cost.</div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 0 14px 18px">
        <a class="btn primary" href="https://forms.gle/YOUR_COMMISSION_FORM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Start a Commission</a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="#faq">Read FAQs</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card" aria-labelledby="care-h" style="padding:18px">
      <div class="section-head"><h2 id="care-h">Materials & Care</h2><p>Made for snuggles and display.</p></div>
      <ul>
        <li>Premium acrylic/cotton yarns; hypoallergenic, pet-safe stuffing.</li>
        <li>Spot clean with cool water + mild soap; air dry. Avoid machine wash.</li>
        <li>Not intended for children under 3 (safety eyes are not really that safe).</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="faq" aria-labelledby="faq-h">
      <div class="section-head"><h2 id="faq-h">FAQ</h2><p>Your top questions, answered.</p></div>
      <details>
        <summary>How big are your pieces?</summary>
        <p>As big or as small as you want them to be. You are paying for my time and mostly yarn — the only limit is likely your pocketbook.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Do you ship outside the US?</summary>
        <p>Shipping is available at shipping costs. If you’re international, note it on the form and I’ll see what’s possible.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I rush an order?</summary>
        <p>Sometimes! Add your date in the form and I’ll confirm what’s realistic before you pay.</p>
      </details>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <small>© <span id="yr"></span> ParkerPixiePaws • Made with coziness in Madison, WI</small>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('yr').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
